                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-186-18580104 t18580104-186-punishment-28"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">POWELL</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18580104-186-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
